AD_COLUMN.NAME: Pendinglines
AD_COLUMN.ENTITY_ALIAS: case when l.searchKey = 'N' then 0 when l.searchKey = 'I' then ic.notinvoicedlines when (l.searchKey = 'O' and ic.deliveredQuantity < ic.orderedQuantity) then 0 else ic.pendinglines end

AD_COLUMN.NAME: Notinvoicedlines
AD_COLUMN.ENTITY_ALIAS: case when l.searchKey = 'N' then 0 when (l.searchKey = 'O' and ic.deliveredQuantity < ic.orderedQuantity) then ic.amountlines else ic.notinvoicedlines end
